Function Documentation

void flusspferd::load_properties_functions ( object  o = global()  ) 

Load the properties function Object.defineProperty and Object.defineProperties modelled after [[DefineOwnProperty]] from the ES6 specification.

Parameters:
o The container (must contain an Object property) to load the functions into.
